title: Ranji Trophy: Pacer Dhawal Kulkarni's fifer gives Mumbai advantage over Baroda
text:
*Vadodra:* Pacer Dhawal Kulkarni took five wickets as Mumbai reduced Baroda to 345 for nine on Day Three of their Ranji Trophy match here on Saturday.
*Mumbai pacer Dhawal Kulkarni*
